translations: v.（使）撞击，碰撞；（使飞机）坠毁
n.猛炸；撞击；事故（坠机、撞车等）；轰炸

phrs.translation: 飞机坠毁, 普朗, 火箭探测计画
华普郎寺, 或者华普郎寺

sentences.sentence: One of the boys has been careless enough to prang up his girl friend.
sentences.translation: 其中一个男孩太大意了，竟使他的女朋友怀了孕。

sentences.sentence: Darling, now do not get angry with me but I had a bit of a prang with a truck today.
sentences.translation: 亲爱的，可别跟我生气啊，不过呢，我今天和一辆卡车剐上了。

sentences.sentence: When the first Prang raids came from the northwestern area of Fal, the Maro of Rhew was formed as a safe haven from these terrible raiders traveling on winged beasts.
sentences.translation: 当第一个Prang袭击来自总装区的西北部，是Rhew马络的是作为一个安全攻略翼兽乘坐从这些可怕的避风港。
